title: 145: The Snack Haul Episode (May ’21 Edition)
itunes:title: The Snack Haul Episode (May ’21 Edition)
description: In this episode, Lisa and the gang are trying a lot of snacks. And spoiler alert: All were pretty well received! They tried snacks like cheese puffs, everything-bagel seasoned crackers, low-carb tortillas, INCREDIBLE new dried fruit snacks, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, they sample a BRAND-NEW peanut butter treat from PASOKIN! So stop everything and push play now. Then head on over to the Foodcast page for a list of products mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: We raided the Hungry Girl pantry for a killer snack haul on this week’s episode of Chew the Right Thing!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
